there, weren't you?

352
00:23:42,521 --> 00:23:45,123
Oh, yes. For more years
than I care to remember.

353
00:23:45,190 --> 00:23:47,893
Why didn't you protect me?

354
00:23:47,959 --> 00:23:50,996
