374
00:25:00,298 --> 00:25:03,201
Mother, please...

375
00:25:03,268 --> 00:25:05,904
Are you?

376
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:10,542
No.

377
00:25:10,609 --> 00:25:13,645
No, I'm not shocked.

378
00:25:16,648 --> 00:25:18,950
Have you told Barry?

379
00:25:19,017 --> 00:25:21,119
