office as soon as we get home.

474
00:30:34,365 --> 00:30:37,268
I don't want the
kids to ever know

475
00:30:37,335 --> 00:30:38,946
the awful things their
grandfather did to me.

476
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:41,272
I'd feel so ashamed!

477
00:30:41,339 --> 00:30:44,909
